            "text": "Integrate BGE M3 via RESTful API endpoints, specifying the model ID as \"bge-m3-fp16\". Use batch processing to minimize request counts—aim for 32-128 sequences per batch to balance latency and cost. Implement error handling for rate limits and timeouts, and validate embedding outputs against expected dimensions."
